rt two of a three part series*\\n\\nI have been thinking about what is the core competency of leadership within a company, and what principles form the structure of the C-suite. I had an eight month internship at Tesla in 2018. There I became a fan of Elon…\\n\\n## [The Foundational Matrix of Companies](https://akeredoluoluwole.medium.com/the-foundational-matrix-of-companies-20675ce198c9?source=user_profile---------4-------------------------------)\\n\\n*This is the first of a three part series on this topic.*\\n\\nI’ve been thinking about where I fit in my company and what role and responsibilities I want to have. That got me thinking about what roles and responsibilities are there to have. …\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640824882,\"title\":\"Akeredolu Oluwole Alaba – Medium\"},\"digest\":\"QGgrfE94EDLztDkpnOIough6_a5WI4k_YFly4s5AyOw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x34E27bb83d081ddfdA3dCBA5503555CAC89D7169\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RdeRUjoAIzijlloChKuS2_Gy-IhCUC44EL464PJqDjw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FuydOSAeCZ9pA34nLOQ2oca6RbERqI-WDvi9GUExZ7A\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"SipYjPBY4YXnRfZIcPinKPBH7ME6vzQCCGYpITk9gi_uBbx56fBW9GCpO21zzO8Jy5QkrwWGAJ3zNCx-BRsVwQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x6a2fb253e0d4dcc8774da27773e03eacd49c6a471f9bb7d32af22611988b3534626738165e22496aefe8ca910fc6687f93b85127fce86c3e072b44ddacf73dee1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RdeRUjoAIzijlloChKuS2_Gy-IhCUC44EL464PJqDjw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FuydOSAeCZ9pA34nLOQ2oca6RbERqI-WDvi9GUExZ7A\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"QGgrfE94EDLztDkpnOIough6_a5WI4k_YFly4s5AyOw\"}"